<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-vi">be <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bi;biː/    美 /bi/  </p>
<p>(现在式am,is,are；过去式was,were；现在分词being；过去分词been)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>是；成为：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The world is round. 
地球是圆的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What are you going to be when you grow up? 
你长大后打算干什么？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>有：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>there be:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Where there is a will, there is a way.
有志者事竟成。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There must be something wrong.
肯定出事了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[表示时间] 是；于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The next match will be at 3 o’clock. 
下一场比赛将于3点钟开始。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>在；存在：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The lamp is on the table. 
灯在桌子上。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>停留；逗留；保持…状态：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They’re here till Christmas. 
他们在这里一直逗留到圣诞节。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The economy is in a terrible condition. 
经济非常不景气。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.★ <strong>出席；到场：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Were you at the party yesterday? 
昨天你去参加聚会了吗?</p></div>

<h4 id="7">7.★ <strong>[用于完成时] 前往；造访：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have you ever been to Beijing? 
你去过北京吗？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Fast food______(be) full of fat and salt.   （2017 全国）  </li>
<li>The publication of Great Expectations, which______(be) both widely reviewed and highly praised strengthened Dickens’ status as a leading novelist.   （2017 江苏改）  </li>
<li>Confucius believed knives would remind people of killings and <strong><em>_</em></strong> (be) too violent for use at the table.  （2016 全国）  </li>
<li>Albert Einstein was born in 1879. As a child, few people guessed that he  <strong><em>_</em></strong>(be) a famous scientist whose theories would change the world.  （2015 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. is  2. was  3. were  4.  was going to / would be  </p></div>